    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The color of this marble ranges from yellow, light brown, and pink to deep red. It originates not from Numidia proper, but from the mountains of Algeria and Mauritania.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
